Boruta is a text file database with stack based query language

This is an exploration of an idea where a text file is a database
presented in humanreadable form that is easy and safe to edit by hand.

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Database_model
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Relational_model
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Codd%27s_12_rules
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flat-file_database


USAGE

	> db_file LOAD
	1
	> table0 TABLE id name updated_at CREATE
	3
	> table0 TABLE id 0 name Gomez INSERT id 1 name Diego INSERT id 2 name Milten INSERT
	3
	> table0 TABLE id 0 GT updated_at NULL EQ name SELECT
	name
	Diego
	Milten
	2
	> table0 TABLE id 1 LEQ updated_at 2025 UPDATE
	2
	> table0 TABLE * SELECT
	id  name    updated_at
	0   Gomez   2025
	1   Diego   2025
	2   Milten  ---
	3
	> table0 TABLE updated_at 2025 EQ DELETE
	2
	> table0 TABLE * SELECT
	id  name    updated_at
	2   Milten  ---
	1
	> table0 TABLE updated_at DROP
	1
	> table0 TABLE * DROP
	2
	> table0 TABLE DROP
	1
	> optional_file_path SAVE
	1
	> UNLOAD
	0
